# ARIA Agent — Cursor Rules
# Read this file first, every session, before doing anything.

---

## What is ARIA
Autonomous Rope Intelligence Architecture — wall-mounted lead climbing auto-belay device.
Targets the US market gap in lead climbing automation. Open source. Provisional patent filed.
Built by Jonathan Kofman (Northeastern MEng Advanced & Intelligent Manufacturing + Georgia Tech OMSCS).
Hardware not yet arrived — Phase 2–3: software, PID, and voice first.

